cat << EOF
Stratagus is a free cross-platform real-time strategy gaming engine. It includes support for playing 
over the internet/LAN, or playing a computer opponent. The engine is configurable and can be used to 
create games with a wide-range of features specific to your needs. See the data sets page for a list 
of current games using the stratagus engine.
EOF
